  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "2. Cut the fermented naan bread into bite-sized pieces.",
    "3. In a bowl, mix together pistachios, coconut milk, lime juice, ginger, garlic, and cilantro.",
    "4. Add the naan pieces to the bowl and toss to coat with the pistachio mixture.",
    "5. Season with salt to taste.",
    "6. Bake in the preheated oven for 10-12 minutes, or until crispy.",
    "7. Serve warm with additional pistachios on top, if desired."
